Name: SolarLunix
AboutMe:
I originally went to college for Genetic Engineering, but because American Colleges are so expensive I wasn't able to finish my final semester of college. I have since changed my degree to Biology, however, I am still two Liberal Arts courses away from full completion. Technically I have completed all of the biological requirements to my degree.

In my free time I love doing a number of things ranging from working with computers to writing fiction to drawing. I also enjoy taking walks and taking photography - specifically macro.

You can look at some of my photography work on Flicker, under the username SolarLunix. I also do my own blog under the username SolarLunix as well.
